room_title: Escape room "Sherlock" by ROOM 5280 in Denver
room_description:
“When you have eliminated the impossible, whatever remains, however improbable, must be the truth”.
Professor James Moriarty and his ally are planning a new crime! There are bombs hidden in different parts of London Underground. You have 60 minutes to visit Moriarty’s office, identify his ally, locate the bombs and escape!
